01:35:31,021 --> 01:35:32,602
It gives me hope for mankind.

1031
01:35:33,202 --> 01:35:34,683
He reminds me of my father.

1032
01:35:34,723 --> 01:35:39,624
He uses a lot of common sense, but I'm sure he has more than a sixth grade education.

