01:36:41,938 --> 01:36:43,559
I apologize again, Mr. Castaneda.

1046
01:36:44,439 --> 01:36:45,360
It's okay.

1047
01:36:45,540 --> 01:36:47,501
I believe I remember the key point.

1048
01:36:47,541 --> 01:36:48,802
Mr. Starella brought up

