01:36:50,123 --> 01:36:58,708
it'll probably be a $400, $500 increase in that real estate tax, I presume he meant.

1050
01:36:59,589 --> 01:37:04,171
And he's probably right on from the last couple of years standing in a row.

1051
01:37:04,191 --> 01:37:08,814
It seems like my real estate tax has gone up $400 annually.

